[{"location":"markets.html#The-Markets-Module","page":"Reference API","title":"The Markets Module","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"markets.html","page":"Reference API","title":"Reference API","text":"Markets","category":"page"},{"location":"markets.html#Markets","page":"Reference API","title":"Markets","text":"Markets - Solve Economic Equilibrium problems\n\nSolve Market equilibrium problems of arbitrary p products and r regions\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"module"},{"location":"markets.html#Module-Index","page":"Reference API","title":"Module Index","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"markets.html","page":"Reference API","title":"Reference API","text":"Modules = [Markets]\nOrder   = [:constant, :type, :function, :macro]","category":"page"},{"location":"markets.html#Detailed-API","page":"Reference API","title":"Detailed API","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"markets.html","page":"Reference API","title":"Reference API","text":"Modules = [Markets]\nOrder   = [:constant, :type, :function, :macro]","category":"page"},{"location":"markets.html#Markets.solveEquilibrium-NTuple{15, Any}","page":"Reference API","title":"Markets.solveEquilibrium","text":"solveEquilibrium\n\nSolve an economic equilibrium by passing elasticities parameters of CD-form supply/demand curves.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"model_description.html#Model-description","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html#Explicit-regional-trade-version","page":"Model description","title":"Explicit regional trade version","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":"Current status: This model returns a \"Too few degrees of freedom\" error Todo: (a) make it working :-); (b) add transport costs, policies, exogenous region and exogenous independent variables in the supply/demand functions; (c) estimate parameters (stochastic gradient descent with norm-1 - à la Lasso - penalty for sparce coefficients ??)","category":"page"},{"location":"model_description.html#Sets","page":"Model description","title":"Sets","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":": p: products (with alias pin)\n: r: regions (with aliases rfrom and rto)","category":"page"},{"location":"model_description.html#Variables","page":"Model description","title":"Variables","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":": sc_pr: Composite supply (quantity)\n: dc_pr: Composite demand (quantity)\n: pcs_pr: Composite supply price\n: pds_pr: Composite demand price\n: s_prfromrto: Supply of product p from region rfrom to region rto\n: d_prfromrto: Demmand of product p coming from region rfrom in region rto\n: pl_pr: Local market price for product p in region r","category":"page"},{"location":"model_description.html#Parameters","page":"Model description","title":"Parameters","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":": ϵs_prpin: elasticity of the (composite) supply of p with respect to the (composite) price of pin in region r\n: ϵd_prpin: elasticity of the (composite) demand of p with respect to the (composite) price of pin in region r\n: consts_pr: constant coefficient of the composite supply function for product p in region r\n: constd_pr: constant coefficient of the composite supply function for product p in region r\n: a_prrto: share parameter of the supply of product p from r to rto\n: b_prfromr: share parameter of the demand of product p in region r coming from region rfrom\n: ϵts_p: trade elasticity of the supply of product p \n: ϵtd_p: trade elasticity of the demand of product p","category":"page"},{"location":"model_description.html#Constraints-(equations)","page":"Model description","title":"Constraints (equations)","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":"Composite supply [p,r] : sc_pr = consts_pr * prod_pin pcs_pinr^ϵs_prpin\nComposite demand [p,r] : dc_pr = constd_pr * prod_pin pcd_pinr^ϵd_prpin\nComposite supply aggregation [p,r] : sc_pr =  (sum_rto a_prrto* s_prrto^ϵts_p)^1ϵts_p\nComposite demand aggregation [p,r] : dc_pr =  (sum_rfrom b_prfromr* s_prfromr^ϵtd_p)^1ϵtd_p\nSupply by destination [p,r] : s_prrto =  a_prrto * fracpcs_prpl_prto^frac11-ϵts_p\nDemand from origin [p,r] : d_prfromr =  b_prfromr * fracpcd_prpl_prfrom^frac11-ϵtd_p\nSupply monetary budget [p,r] : $ pcs{p,r} * sc{p,r}  =  \\sum{rto} pl{p,rto} * s_{p,r,rto}$\nDemand monetary budget [p,r] : $ pcd{p,r} * dc{p,r}  =  \\sum{rfrom} pl{p,rfrom} * s_{p,rfrom,r}$\nPhysical balance [p, r] :  sum_rto s_prrto =  sum_rfrom d_prfromr","category":"page"},{"location":"model_description.html#Objective","page":"Model description","title":"Objective","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":"min sum_prfromrto (d_prfromrto - s_prfromrto)^2","category":"page"},{"location":"model_description.html#Implicit-regional-trade-version","page":"Model description","title":"Implicit regional trade version","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":"Current status: Model correctly solves (very quickly!) but it doesn't return the information on the amount of production allocated to own region or exported not the share of demand satisfied by own production or imported.","category":"page"},{"location":"model_description.html#Sets-2","page":"Model description","title":"Sets","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":"| p: products (with alias pin)\n. r: regions (with aliases rin and rto)","category":"page"},{"location":"model_description.html#Variables-2","page":"Model description","title":"Variables","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":"→ s_pr: Supply (quantity)\n▷ d_pr: Demand (quantity)\n➔ p_pr: Price","category":"page"},{"location":"model_description.html#Parameters-2","page":"Model description","title":"Parameters","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":"➜ ϵs_prpinrin: elasticity of the (total) supply of product p in region r with respect to the price of product pin in region rin\n➝ ϵd_prpinrin: elasticity of the (total) demand of product p in region r with respect to the price of product pin in region rin\n➞ consts_{p,r}: constant coefficient of the supply function for product p in region r\nconstd_{p,r}: constant coefficient of the supply function for product p in region r","category":"page"},{"location":"model_description.html#Constraints-(equations)-2","page":"Model description","title":"Constraints (equations)","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":"Total supply [p,r] : s_pr = consts_pr * prod_pinrin p_pinr^ϵs_prpinrin\nTotal demand [p,r] : d_pr = constd_pr * prod_pinrin p_pinr^ϵd_prpinrin","category":"page"},{"location":"model_description.html#Objective-2","page":"Model description","title":"Objective","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"model_description.html","page":"Model description","title":"Model description","text":"min sum_pr (d_pr - s_pr)^2","category":"page"},{"location":"index.html#Markets.jl","page":"Index","title":"Markets.jl","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"index.html","page":"Index","title":"Index","text":"Documentation for the Markets.jl Julia Package","category":"page"},{"location":"index.html","page":"Index","title":"Index","text":"Github: https://github.com/sylvaticus/Markets.jl","category":"page"},{"location":"index.html","page":"Index","title":"Index","text":"Warning: prealpha status","category":"page"}]
